
1.create SERVICE ACCOUNT:

gcloud iam service-accounts create NAME --description="cli created sa" --display-name="NAME"


2.Adding USER to SERVICE ACCOUNT and Attaching a ROLE:

gcloud iam service-accounts add-iam-policy-binding [SA-EMAIL] --member=user:[OTHER-USER-EMAIL] --role=roles/iam.serviceAccountUser (ROLE-NAME)
